This file has no extension.

A file browser should handle extensionless files gracefully,
ideally falling back to plain text display. Common examples
of extensionless files include:

  - Makefile
  - Dockerfile
  - LICENSE
  - Procfile
  - Vagrantfile
  - .gitignore (dotfile, no extension)

The MIME type should default to application/octet-stream or
text/plain depending on content sniffing.
